 - install scrapy packages for python 

- scraper dependent on cryptography, lxml python packages

- scraper dependent on libssl-dev, openssl-devel, libxml2-dev, libxslt1-dev

 - to run, make sure to be in same directory as scrapy project

 - run on command line:

	scrapy crawl arco_pls

 - to export results to csv file for convenient viewing of obtained data:
	
	scrapy crawl arco_pls -o results.csv -t csv
